# Fjällkompis — environment variables (build-time, Vite `VITE_*` convention).
#
# Copy to `.env.local` (git-ignored) and fill in values. NEVER put a real
# value in this file, in any tracked file, or in documentation.

# Thunderforest Map Tiles API key — enables the ONLINE-ONLY
# "Thunderforest Outdoors" comparison basemap on the Map screen
# (docs/maps/thunderforest-outdoors-benchmark.md). Leave empty to keep the
# option unavailable; nothing else in the app depends on it.
#
# SECURITY: Vite inlines VITE_* variables into the built JavaScript. The key
# is therefore VISIBLE in the deployed bundle and in browser tile-request
# URLs — build-time injection only keeps it out of the repository. Restrict
# the key to your origins in the Thunderforest dashboard.
VITE_THUNDERFOREST_API_KEY=

# Optional override for satellite-archive hosting (rarely needed — see
# docs/DEVELOPMENT.md "Satellite imagery layer").
# VITE_SATELLITE_URL=
